  <!-- Estrategia de apoyo si muchos estudiantes respondieron incorrectamente -->
  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="apoyo-cool-titulo"/></title><p>[++++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Before the warm-up, have students discuss strategies for partitioning the diagram in the cool-down into 8 equal parts.</p>
  </paragraphs>

</postlude>

</project>